<br>
<b>There is no Snow Bunny Hood. It does not exist. It never has. Please don't waste any more of your time, finances or rare resources trying to make this!</b><br>
<br>
<img src=http://www.thegamevine.com/~Dashing_Rogue/mof/bunbun.jpg><br>
<br>
The clever screenshot and item card came from the very talented hands of Syrinne, a druid for my guild (and safehouse regular). They were not created with the intent of fooling anyone other than her guildmates in Mark of Fire.<br>
<br>
She was pretty clever about it too, slipping the shot in among a bunch of random screenshots she's taken lately. Since most of the other things in the post were real, we bought into the existance of the Bunny hood, hook, line and proverbial sinker.<br>
<br>
The overly wimpy stats on the item only lended further credibility to the hoax. After all, most other hoax items of the past, all focused on uber stats, not...cuteness! With bunnies being introduced into velious, and new helms like the Wolf hat, somehow this felt entirely believable!<br>
<br>
A few mysterious 'new art' patches at the same time she created this, only added more credibility to it's existance. <br>
<br>
Syrinne revealed the truth of the hood to us shortly after, simultaneously breaking all our hearts, and making us fall over laughing at how easilly we bought into it. But somewhere during all of this, Halen posted the images to the safehouse (I'll leave it up to the reader to decide if Halen knew the truth of the hood when he posted it)<br>
<br>
It shouldn't have surprised us how many folks cross servers fell for it the same way we had, but it did. And from there, it spread like wildfire to nearly every EQ board we could find. The elusive snow bunny hood captured the imaginations of all of us.<br>
<br>
We were going to reveal the truth then, but being the sorry lot of dreamers we are, we thought that maybe if enough of us believed in the existance of the Bunny Hood, somehow, someone at Verant would agree this was the neatest thing ever and add it.<br>
<br>
I know, it's naive, but that's the wonder of dreams. <br>
<br>
But then, the dream became an obsession. Things started escallating wildly. Folks on every server started combining anything they could think of to recreate the hood. Visitors started coming to Tholuxe to trick the recipe out of us. I started personally getting tells from strangers offering me everythng from ultra rare items to um...romantic favors for the secret. <i>(Oh how I prayed for the hood to be real those moments!)</i> ;)<br>
<br>
But seriously it came to our attention that some folks were blowing some really expensive/rare type items in futile combinations, and this is where we felt we had to draw the line. Thus this post.<br>
<br>
I'm sure some of you will be quite mad over this, but understand we're just as sad as you. In our hearts, the bunny hood is real. (And please don't blame Syrinne! The joke was never meant to leave our guild boards.)<br>
<br>
So in closing, stop trying to make this. The thousands of Snow Bunnies being slaughtered daily will thank you.<br>
<br>
<b>-Cutlass Jack, Mark of Fire Guildmaster.</b><br>
<br>
<i>P.S. Verant, if you're reading this, add the hood already! Think of how many Velious expansions you'd sell if that was the only way to see the graphic!</i><br>
<br>
